### conventions.md
```markdown
# Project Conventions

## File Naming
- Components: PascalCase.tsx
- Hooks: useFeatureName.ts
- Utils: camelCase.ts

## Directory Structure
- src/components/ - Reusable components
- src/screens/ - Screen components
- src/hooks/ - Custom hooks
- src/services/ - API services

## Import Order
1. React/React Native
2. Third-party libraries
3. Project imports (absolute)
4. Relative imports
```

### rules.md
```markdown
# Project-Specific Rules

## Must Follow
- All new components must have tests
- Use theme colors, no hardcoded values
- Props interface required for all components

## Avoid
- Inline styles (use StyleSheet)
- Direct API calls in components (use services)
- Magic numbers (use constants)
```

## Loading Priority

```
1. Project context (.cursor/project-contexts/[name]/)
2. Aura Frog rules (.cursor/rules/)
3. Default conventions
```

## Cross-Agent Collaboration

- **All Agents** - Provides project context
- **Development Agents** - Enforces conventions
- **QA Agent** - Applies testing rules

